Ranger Help for: call follower
================================

SYNTAX:      call
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   5
BASE SP:     20
SKILL TYPE:  husbandry

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to summon their bonded animal follower to
their side, regardless of where the follower currently is. The follower
will make its way to the Ranger as quickly as it can. The Ranger must
have previously bonded with a follower for this skill to work. If the
follower has died and the Ranger has not yet called a new one, this
skill will attempt to attract a new companion based on the Ranger's
primary terrain.
